      "text": [
        ": سَأَلْتُ أَبَا اَلْحَسَنِ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ عَنِ اَلْجُمُعَةِ فِي اَلسَّفَرِ مَا أَقْرَأُ فِيهِمَا قَالَ «اِقْرَأْ فِيهِمَا «قُلْ هُوَ اَللّٰهُ أَحَدٌ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1226 - Safwan ibn Yahya narrated from Ali ibn Yaqtin who said:\n\"I asked Imam Abu al-Hasan (as) about the Jumu’ah prayer while traveling. What should I recite in them?\"\nImam (as) said: \"Recite in them 'Qul Huwa Allahu Ahad' (Surah Al-Ikhlas).\""
        ]
      }
    },
